snippet.title: Cute Farm Hospital Video Tutorial(Walkthrough)
snippet.description:
Cute Farm Hospital is an adventure that will be accepted by many boy and girls. It is a story about a girl that came on the farm with one mission: to help the cute animals. Be her assistant and take good car for the animals.
Play the game at: http://www.horse-games.org/Cute_Farm_Hospital.html
